# Sample quotations live here for the smoke:quotation script. The three
# quotation_00*.pdf files committed alongside this .gitignore are
# synthetic fixtures used for reproducible demo prep — they're allowlisted
# below. Any OTHER PDF/image you drop into this directory stays local-only
# (they may contain real client names, amounts, or addresses).
*.pdf
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
!.gitkeep
!quotation_001.pdf
!quotation_002.pdf
!quotation_003.pdf
